<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='8905:8920'>五子之歌第三　夏書　孔氏傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='8920:8954'>太康失邦<span class='krp-note'>啓子也盤于遊田不恤民/事爲羿所逐不得反國</span>昆弟五人須于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='8954:8994'>洛汭作五子之歌<span class='krp-note'>太康五弟與其母待太康於洛水之/北怨其不反故作歌五子名字書傳</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='8994:9038'><span class='krp-note'>無聞仲康蓋其一也須馬云止/也汭如銳反本又作内音同</span>五子之歌<span class='krp-note'>啓之五子/因以名篇</span>太</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='9038:9076'>康尸位以逸豫<span class='krp-note'>尸主也主以尊位爲逸䂊不勤/逸本又作佾豫本又作忬音同</span>滅厥德</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='9076:9114'>黎民咸貳<span class='krp-note'>君䘮其德則衆民皆貳心/矣黎力兮反䘮息浪反</span>乃盤遊無度<span class='krp-note'>盤/樂</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='9114:9142'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '003-12a' );" name="003-12a" class="pb">[003-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='9142:9176'><span class='krp-note'>游逸無法度盤歩干反本/或作槃度如字樂音洛</span>畋于有洛之表十旬弗反</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='9176:9212'><span class='krp-note'>洛水之表水之南十日曰旬/田獵過百日不還畋音田</span>有窮后羿因民弗忍距于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='9212:9253'>河<span class='krp-note'>有窮國名羿諸侯名距太康於河不得入/國遂廢之羿五計反徐胡細反距音巨</span>厥弟五人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='9253:9285'>御其母以從<span class='krp-note'>御侍也言從畋從如/字或作才用反非</span>徯于洛之汭五子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='9285:9323'>咸怨<span class='krp-note'>待太康怨其乆畋/失國徯胡啓反</span>述大禹之戒以作歌<span class='krp-note'>𫐠循也/歌以叙</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='9323:9354'><span class='krp-note'>怨</span>其一曰皇祖有訓民可近不可下<span class='krp-note'>皇君也君祖/禹有訓戒近</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='9354:9399'><span class='krp-note'>謂親之下謂失分近/附近之近分扶問反</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>民可近不可下太甲/下無輕民事惟難</span>民惟邦本</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='9399:9427'>本固邦寜<span class='krp-note'>言人君當固/民以安國</span>予視天下愚夫愚婦一能</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='9427:9456'>勝予<span class='krp-note'>言能畏敬小民/所以得衆心</span>一人三失怨豈在明不見是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='9456:9493'>圖<span class='krp-note'>三失過非一也不見是謀備其/微三如字又息暫反見賢遍反</span>予臨兆民懔乎若</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='9493:9521'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '003-12b' );" name="003-12b" class="pb">[003-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='9521:9549'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '003-12b' );" name="003-12b" class="pb">[003-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='9549:9577'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '003-12b' );" name="003-12b" class="pb">[003-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='9577:9618'><span class='krp-note'>㣧國之君受王命/往征之㣧國名</span>㣧征<span class='krp-note'>奉辭罰/罪曰征</span>惟仲康肇位四海<span class='krp-note'>羿/廢</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='9618:9662'><span class='krp-note'>太康而立其弟仲康/爲天子肇音兆下同</span>㣧侯命掌六師<span class='krp-note'>仲康命㣧侯掌王/六師爲大司馬</span>〇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='9662:9697'>重意<span class='krp-note'>掌六師周官/篇統六師</span>羲和廢厥職酒荒于厥邑<span class='krp-note'>舎其職/官還其</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='9697:9736'><span class='krp-note'>私邑以酒迷亂不/修其業舎音捨</span>㣧后承王命徂征<span class='krp-note'>徂徃也就其/私邑往討之</span>告</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='9736:9764'>于衆曰嗟予有衆<span class='krp-note'>誓勑/之</span>聖有謨訓明徴定保<span class='krp-note'>徴/證</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='9764:9800'><span class='krp-note'>也保安也聖人所謀之教訓/爲丗明證所以定國安家</span>先王克謹天戒臣人克有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='9800:9834'>常憲<span class='krp-note'>言君能慎戒臣/能奉有常法</span>百官修輔厥后惟明明<span class='krp-note'>修職/輔君</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='9834:9870'><span class='krp-note'>君臣/俱明</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>厥后惟明明太/甲下惟明明后</span>毎歲孟春遒人以木鐸徇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='9870:9910'>于路<span class='krp-note'>道人宣令之官木鐸金鈴木舌所以/振文教遒在由反鐸待洛反鈴音令</span>官師相規工</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='9910:9954'>執藝事以諌<span class='krp-note'>官衆衆官更相規闕百工各執其所治技藝/以諌諌失常藝本又作蓺更音庚技其綺反</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='9954:9982'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '003-13a' );" name="003-13a" class="pb">[003-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='9982:10010'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '003-14a' );" name="003-14a" class="pb">[003-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='10010:10051'><span class='krp-note'>甚干/犯也</span>政典曰先時者殺無赦<span class='krp-note'>政典夏后爲政之典籍若/周官六卿之治典先時謂</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='10051:10099'><span class='krp-note'>曆象之法四時節氣弦望晦朔先天時則罪死無赦先/悉薦反又如字注先時先天同赦時夜反治直吏反</span>不及</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='10099:10139'>時者殺無赦<span class='krp-note'>不及謂曆象後天時雖治其官苟有先/後之差則無赦况廢官乎後胡豆反</span>今</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l259' data-llen='10139:10175'>予以爾有衆奉將天罰<span class='krp-note'>將行也奉王命行王誅謂/殺湎淫之身立其賢子弟</span>重意</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l260' data-llen='10175:10225'><span class='krp-note'>今予以爾有衆奉將天罰湯誓爾尚輔予一人致天之罰/泰誓上以爾有衆底天之罰泰誓下奉予一人恭行天罰</span>爾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l261' data-llen='10225:10253'>衆士同力王室尚弼予欽承天子威命<span class='krp-note'>以天子威/命督其士</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l262' data-llen='10253:10295'><span class='krp-note'>衆使/用命</span>重言<span class='krp-note'>爾衆士三本篇/二泰誓下一</span>火炎崐岡玉石俱焚<span class='krp-note'>山脊曰/岡崐山</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l263' data-llen='10295:10336'><span class='krp-note'>出玉言火逸而/害玉崐音昆</span>天吏逸德烈于猛火<span class='krp-note'>逸過也天王之吏/爲過惡之德其傷</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l264' data-llen='10336:10377'><span class='krp-note'>害天下甚於火之害玉/猛火烈矣又烈於火</span>殱厥渠魁脅從罔治<span class='krp-note'>殱滅渠大/魁帥也指</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l265' data-llen='10377:10420'><span class='krp-note'>謂羲和罪人之身其脅從距王師者皆無治/殱子廉反魁苦回反脅虚業反帥色類反</span>舊染汙俗咸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l266' data-llen='10420:10448'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '003-14b' );" name="003-14b" class="pb">[003-14b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l267' data-llen='10448:10496'>與惟新<span class='krp-note'>言其餘人乆染汙俗本無惡心皆與更新一無所問/汙烏故反汙辱之汙又音烏涴泥著物也一音烏卧</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l268' data-llen='10496:10528'><span class='krp-note'>反</span>嗚呼威克厥愛允濟<span class='krp-note'>歎能以威勝所/愛則必有成功</span>愛克厥威</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l269' data-llen='10528:10565'>允罔功<span class='krp-note'>以愛勝威無以/濟衆信無功</span>其爾衆士懋戒哉<span class='krp-note'>言當勉以/用命戒以</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l270' data-llen='10565:10605'><span class='krp-note'>辟戮懋音/茂辟音避</span>重意<span class='krp-note'>懋戒哉大禹謨戒/哉太甲嗣王戒哉</span>自契至于成湯八遷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l271' data-llen='10605:10651'><span class='krp-note'>十四丗/凢八徙國都契悉列/反/殷之始祖八遷八遷之書史唯見四</span>湯始居亳從先王居<span class='krp-note'>契/父</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l272' data-llen='10651:10698'><span class='krp-note'>帝嚳都亳湯自商丘/遷焉故曰從先王居</span>作帝告釐沃<span class='krp-note'>告來居治沃土二篇皆/亡告工毒反沃徐烏酷</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l273' data-llen='10698:10742'><span class='krp-note'>反此五亡篇舊解是夏書馬/鄭之徒以爲商書兩義俱通</span>湯征諸侯<span class='krp-note'>爲夏方伯/得專征伐</span>葛伯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l274' data-llen='10742:10784'>不祀湯始征之<span class='krp-note'>葛國伯爵也廢其土地山川及宗廟神祇/皆不祀湯始伐之伐始於葛祇巨支反</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l275' data-llen='10784:10819'>作湯征<span class='krp-note'>述始征之/義也亡</span>伊尹去亳適夏<span class='krp-note'>伊尹字氏/湯進於桀</span>旣醜有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l276' data-llen='10819:10862'>夏復歸于亳<span class='krp-note'>醜惡其政不能用賢/故退還復扶又反</span>重言<span class='krp-note'>復歸于亳三後/見湯誥太甲上</span>入</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l277' data-llen='10862:10890'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '003-15a' );" name="003-15a" class="pb">[003-15a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l278' data-llen='10890:10922'>自北門乃遇汝鳩汝方<span class='krp-note'>鳩方二人湯之賢/臣不期而會曰遇</span>作汝鳩汝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l279' data-llen='10922:10941'>方<span class='krp-note'>言所以醜夏而還/之意二篇皆亡</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l280' data-llen='10941:10969'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0002', 'SBCK', '003-15b' );" name="003-15b" class="pb">[003-15b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
</p>
